%N A015928 Inverse of 1919th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015928 Periodic with period length 1919. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015928 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015928/b015928.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015928 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1919.
%H A015928 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1800">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1800.
%H A015928 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015928 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015928 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1919,x],{x,0,120}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Mar 21 2026 *)
%o A015928 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1919)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
